## Tipos Globais

```typescript
// types/api.ts
export interface Pagination<T> {
  currentPage: number
  firstPage: number
  lastPage: number
  perPage: number
  total: number      // ← .total (NÃO .meta.total)
  data: T[]
}

export interface IncludeContract {
  include: string           // nome da relação
  fields?: string[]         // colunas específicas (SELECT)
  orderBy?: string[]        // ex: ['name,asc']
  children?: IncludeContract[]  // relações aninhadas
}

export interface RequestParams {
  page?: number
  perPage?: number
  includes?: IncludeContract[]
  filters?: object
  orderBy?: string[]        // ex: ['id,desc']
  withCount?: string[]
  listType?: 'list' | 'pagination'
}
```

## Padrão de Types (Feature-Level)

```typescript
// components/features/orders/types/types.ts
export interface Order {
  id: number
  creatorId: number
  companyId: number
  statusId: number
  sellerId: number
  salesNumber?: string
  customerName: string
  deliveryDate: string
  createdAt: string
  updatedAt: string
  deletedAt?: string

  // Relationships (opcionais — dependem do include)
  creator?: { id: number; firstName: string; lastName: string; fullName: string }
  company?: { id: number; name: string }
  seller?: { id: number; firstName: string; lastName: string; fullName: string }
  status?: { id: number; name: string; color: string }
  notes?: OrderNote[]
  purchases?: Purchase[]
}

export interface OrderFilters {
  search?: string
  status?: number[] | string[]
  sellerId?: number | number[]
  companyId?: number | number[]
  deliveryDate?: string
}
```

## Regras de Organização

| O quê                    | Onde                                        |
| ------------------------ | ------------------------------------------- |
| **Types/Interfaces**     | `features/{feature}/types/types.ts`         |
| **API Resource class**   | `lib/api/resources/{feature}.ts`            |
| **Resource re-exports**  | Types do feature re-exportados              |
| **Global types**         | `types/api.ts` (Pagination, RequestParams)  |
| **User type**            | `types/entities/user.ts`                    |

## Boas Práticas

1. **Um Resource por entidade** — extends HttpClient<T>
2. **Singleton**: `export const entityResource = new EntityResource()`
3. **Types na feature**, re-export no Resource
4. **`includes` com `fields`** — SEMPRE selecionar colunas necessárias
5. **`listType: 'list'`** para lookups (sem paginação)
6. **`orderBy: ['id,desc']`** — formato string array
7. **Pagination**: acessar `.total` diretamente (NÃO `.meta.total`)
8. **Server fetch** para SSR (pages), **Axios** para client components
